<view class="page-shell membership-page">
  <page-header back="{{true}}" title="会员与联系权益" subtitle="每次扣除前明确展示价格、额度和保障规则"></page-header>

  <view class="hero-card membership-hero">
    <view class="hero-grid"></view>
    <view class="membership-kicker">{{activeUntil ? '会员状态' : '当前身份'}}</view>
    <view class="membership-title">{{activeUntil ? activeUntil : '普通用户'}}</view>
    <view class="membership-desc">会员期内可无限解锁合作方联系方式，也可在合作方详情页按次解锁。</view>
    <view class="quota-row">
      <view><text>{{balance}}</text><label>钱包余额</label></view>
      <view><text>{{activeUntil ? '∞' : '0'}}</text><label>会员期内解锁</label></view>
      <view><text>{{activeUntil ? '∞' : '0'}}</text><label>按次购买可用</label></view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section">
    <view class="section-head">
      <text class="section-title">选择权益</text>
      <text class="section-action" bindtap="openRules">保障规则 ></text>
    </view>
    <view class="plan-list">
      <view
        class="card plan-card {{selectedPlan === item.key ? 'selected' : ''}}"
        wx:for="{{plans}}"
        wx:key="key"
        data-key="{{item.key}}"
        bindtap="selectPlan"
      >
        <view class="plan-radio"><view></view></view>
        <view class="plan-copy">
          <view class="plan-name">{{item.name}} <text wx:if="{{item.badge}}">{{item.badge}}</text></view>
          <view class="plan-desc">{{item.description}}</view>
        </view>
        <view class="plan-price">{{item.price}}</view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="card newcomer-card">
    <view class="newcomer-badge">NEW</view>
    <view>
      <view class="newcomer-title">新人优惠只在支付成功后核销</view>
      <text>取消支付不会消耗资格，优惠金额和有效期会在付款前明确展示。</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section">
    <view class="section-head">
      <text class="section-title">权益如何使用</text>
    </view>
    <view class="card rule-card">
      <view class="rule-row"><text>1</text><view><view>打开真实主体详情</view><label>先查看能力、案例和认证，再决定是否联系</label></view></view>
      <view class="rule-row"><text>2</text><view><view>确认本次权益</view><label>优先使用会员额度，不足时再选择按次购买</label></view></view>
      <view class="rule-row"><text>3</text><view><view>支付成功后解锁</view><label>支付结果以服务端查单为准，未知状态不会重复扣款</label></view></view>
      <view class="rule-row"><text>4</text><view><view>无效信息可申诉</view><label>核实后退回次数或额度，并复核被投诉主体</label></view></view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section">
    <view class="section-head">
      <text class="section-title">使用记录</text>
    </view>
    <view class="card inline-empty">暂无权益获得、消耗或退回记录</view>
  </view>

  <button class="btn-primary purchase-button" loading="{{purchasing || loading}}" disabled="{{purchasing || loading}}" bindtap="purchase">
    确认开通会员
  </button>
</view>
